{"tid":987360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱竹枝代鋼筋亦安全","createTime":"2019-01-19T08:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T11:47:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d42d791a48616c4b928efe294acea91d3f8a4b1b","tid":987360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190119/20594685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F20594685&d=BzfQOgOuAR39WBJe82ZQjb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=265974f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F20594685&h=06bf37d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190119/20594685</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月19日 <br />\n<br />\n稱竹枝代鋼筋亦安全<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190119/large/18779975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190119%2Flarge%2F18779975.jpg&h=659bc0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙中綫聆訊月底結案陳詞；圖為紅磡站地盤。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】委員會委聘的專家Don McQuillan昨作供，與港鐵及禮頓委聘的專家不約而同接納供應商人和早前的測試結果，認為鋼筋扭入螺絲帽60%已非常安全。McQuillan更批評政府定期公佈紅磡站開鑿石屎檢測是誤導公眾，聲言東西走廊月台層板底部根本毋須使用鋼筋，即使以「竹枝」取代亦不影響結構完整。<br />\n<br />\nMcQuillan作供時批評政府就鋼筋扭入螺絲帽要37毫米是過於嚴格，強調扭入60%已非常安全。他又指只有部份區域的螺絲帽對結構安全屬關鍵，部份則無關重要。他認為東西走廊月台層板底部不承受拉力，根本毋須使用鋼筋，若只計算關鍵位置的檢測結果，現時只有兩個樣本不合格，指定期公佈開鑿結果誤導公眾及混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：委員會專家：政府定期公佈檢測結果是誤導<br />\n<br />\n指政府荷載測試屬謬誤<br />\n<br />\n代表中科的大狀蘇信恩追問McQuillan，是否認為東西走廊月台層板底部不用任何鋼筋，即使只放入竹枝亦可保持層板結構完整，McQuillan表示正確。<br />\n<br />\nMcQuillan指月台層板的荷載中約九成屬固定的恆載，剩餘8至10%才是列車等活動負載，現時列車已試行，若鋼筋現在無斷裂，將來亦不會斷裂。他認為層板結構安全，仍進行學術計算是浪費資源，政府要做的荷載測試亦屬謬誤。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍雅謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n委員會專家：政府定期公佈檢測結果是誤導<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n斥醫管局報告偏頗　「問嘅嘢都答唔到」　扭腸B父　交新證據追究威院<br />\n<br />\n委員會專家：政府定期公佈檢測結果是誤導"},{"pid":"f7f21b2e800cbc09692a206ff83ab28e19f16bae","tid":987360,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"不如講下要點先唔安全啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e043987ec56c2b3c566dd6d557f1d62b16edacd5","tid":987360,"uid":64601,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"竹枝都得，枝竹都得啦"},{"pid":"3e46ef8eaeed2f2fd03e58799ee5ee8b7aec02f5","tid":987360,"uid":71655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3d6aa01bbcad812ce73e7efc2387cb662b0ed0e","tid":987360,"uid":21553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e043987ec56c2b3c566dd6d557f1d62b16edacd5","tid":987360,"uid":64601,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"竹枝都得，枝竹都得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"枝竹都得，豆腐都得啦"},{"pid":"d587ce2414f3919b3a3dfdac35e8542cc85e43b5","tid":987360,"uid":197157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"安唔安全都好，你唔跟合約／圖則已經錯撚晒<br />\n你覺得冇鋼筋都安全唔早響？係要到依家出撚晒事先講真係多鳩餘"},{"pid":"9f1cab15519e39dcab2572674ad38ccd0ce6d428","tid":987360,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"condom都得"},{"pid":"816f4d7351c3c4a292e13b624fd0c7537193d32c","tid":987360,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"幫禮賓府，中聯辦換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89289652f4995ffb8297805b13b58acae0e6a00","tid":987360,"uid":3399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"點解一時話扭入60%就安全，一時又話根本唔洗鋼根，用竹都得<br />\n<br />\n如果真係用竹都得咁扭1%掂住已經勁過碌竹啦"},{"pid":"dc4266a8b738fb44dfb634215f4fc78124a5d752","tid":987360,"uid":170942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"為咗錢，啲所謂嘅專家可以有幾唔尊重自己嘅終身事業呀？"},{"pid":"8fa044e7ef683b54bbe4840e1de1f21536d9fb93","tid":987360,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"睇錯枝竹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b834fb51c772b00c9025a83d5cecb3c48f68fd","tid":987360,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e043987ec56c2b3c566dd6d557f1d62b16edacd5","tid":987360,"uid":64601,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"竹枝都得，枝竹都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"但係一定要有羊腩,  無羊腩爭好遠."},{"pid":"fa500762a76c2dfec399cad480c3b4c852cdeaea","tid":987360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7f21b2e800cbc09692a206ff83ab28e19f16bae","tid":987360,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"不如講下要點先唔安全啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b1ccf0a852a0ad6409bb6ef5fcd89d0c6531f6","tid":987360,"uid":109531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"以為狗鐵已經痴撚左線<br />\n枝竹都夠膽拎黎起野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef4547fe49e6447baf0b9c1b1bc37c1d5dcd55","tid":987360,"uid":116181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38b834fb51c772b00c9025a83d5cecb3c48f68fd","tid":987360,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e043987ec56c2b3c566dd6d557f1d62b16edacd5","tid":987360,"uid":64601,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"竹枝都得，枝竹都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"但係一定要有羊腩,  無羊腩爭好遠."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"個芡要夠濃味"},{"pid":"9bff47365bd0